        <comments>Optional Choice categorizing the case per AAP Section 0.5.7 verbatim (no Mandatory marker). Values: General Inquiry, Complaint (extensible). Drives which Flow Designer flow handles state transitions: ../flows/general_inquiry_state_machine.xml or ../flows/complaint_state_machine.xml. Used by ../reports/x_casemgmt_all_cases_by_type.xml. Replaces ArkCase CaseFile.caseType (free-form String). Internal forms, the Table API, the scripted REST submission endpoint, and seed cases all populate this field explicitly with one of the supported labels.</comments>
        <create_roles/>
